import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { LinkContainer } from 'react-router-bootstrap';

function Navigation() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="lg">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="/">Ghost Identity Protection</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <LinkContainer to="/">
              <Nav.Link>Dashboard</Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            <LinkContainer to="/vault">
              <Nav.Link>Digital Vault</Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            <LinkContainer to="/policies">
              <Nav.Link>Action Policies</Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            <LinkContainer to="/trusted-contact">
              <Nav.Link>Trusted Contact</Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            <LinkContainer to="/admin">
              <Nav.Link>Admin View</Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Navigation;
